FL_ENDGAME_KO_TRAILS_ENTRY_1_DETAIL = Secure salvage and leather to push Beecher's~n~Hope from a field bench into a true~n~workshop. This is the first real~n~farm-upgrade-return milestone and the gate~n~into broader crafting depth. 지역: West~n~Elizabeth Rewards: 작업대 등급 2, Hub upgrade~n~slot, Map board readiness
