FL_SIMULATED_KO_TRAILS_ENTRY_0_DETAIL = Trace the ledger clues pushing John from~n~Beecher's Hope into Blackwater's contract~n~web. Follow courier scraps, broker notes,~n~and the first frontier leads until the war~n~becomes visible. 지역: West Elizabeth Rewards:~n~Unlock Blackwater contract routing, 개방~n~Beecher's Hope briefing board
