FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_0_DETAIL = Low-end elites and grounded threat growth~n~around West Elizabeth. Enemy: Low-end elites~n~and grounded threat growth around West~n~Elizabeth. Loot: Basic materials, low-end~n~accessories, and clean opening upgrade flow.~n~보스es: Early elite hunts and the first real~n~clues to Silas Redd. Recipes: 등급 1~n~maintenance, simple fitting, first accessory~n~lane. Story: Beecher's Hope raid and~n~Blackwater opening pressure. Routes: West~n~Elizabeth and Great Plains open as the first~n~meaningful farming lanes.
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_0_LABEL = WT 1 | Frontier Stirring | Cleared
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_1_DETAIL = More organized enemies, stronger route~n~presence, and better trait coverage. Enemy:~n~More organized enemies, stronger route~n~presence, and better trait coverage. Loot:~n~Advanced drops, better salvage, and wider~n~broker-grade inputs. 보스es: Silas is~n~defeated, relic bosses begin to matter, and~n~clue-준비됨 threats spread. Recipes: 등급 2~n~tuning, better accessories, and meaningful~n~armory depth. Story: Contract boards, map~n~board, and broader frontier war framing~n~unlock. Routes: New Austin and Lemoyne start~n~becoming serious routes instead of rumors.
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_1_LABEL = WT 2 | 개방 Wounds | 현재
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_2_DETAIL = Named elites widen, boss support packs~n~deepen, and multi-wave pressure becomes~n~central. Enemy: Named elites widen, boss~n~support packs deepen, and multi-wave~n~pressure becomes central. Loot: Rare~n~materials and relic economy items become~n~necessary rather than optional. 보스es: 보스~n~chains deepen and myth-pressure targets stop~n~feeling optional. Recipes: 등급 3 named~n~blueprints, specialist work, and deeper~n~house expansion open. Story: The Surveyor's~n~network starts to become legible instead of~n~rumor-only. Routes: Faction routes, relic~n~lanes, and support stations reshape the~n~travel plan.
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_2_LABEL = WT 3 | Relic War | 잠김
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_3_DETAIL = Late-game traits, heavy pressure, mythic~n~escalation, and more punishing route~n~control. Enemy: Late-game traits, heavy~n~pressure, mythic escalation, and more~n~punishing route control. Loot: Late boss~n~parts, rare caches, and high-end specialist~n~goods dominate value. 보스es: The mastermind~n~network and mythic confrontation path come~n~fully into view. Recipes: 등급 4 boss/relic~n~modifications and war-room-scale support~n~upgrades open. Story: The final act is fully~n~armed and the ranch is directly endangered.~n~Routes: Safe travel is mostly gone; the~n~frontier must be navigated as a campaign~n~map.
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_3_LABEL = WT 4 | Ash Frontier | 잠김
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_4_DETAIL = Post-ending legendary sandbox with endless~n~elite and hunt pressure. Enemy: Post-ending~n~legendary sandbox with endless elite and~n~hunt pressure. Loot: Endless legendary~n~farming and prestige collection routes~n~remain active. 보스es: 보스es return in hunt~n~form and the frontier stays dangerous after~n~the ending. Recipes: Post-ending mastery and~n~repeatable high-risk reward loops stay open.~n~Story: John has ended the war, but not every~n~scar, rumor, or hunt. Routes: Beecher's Hope~n~remains the hub while the whole map stays~n~viable for endless play.
FL_SIMULATED_KO_WORLD_ENTRY_4_LABEL = WT 5 | After The Ledger | 잠김
